const candidateData = $('Code in JavaScript1').item.json;

const prompt = 'Format this candidate's resume professionally. Create a clean, ATS-friendly resume.

' +
'CANDIDATE DATA:
' +
'Name: ' + candidateData.name + '
' +
'Email: ' + candidateData.email + '
' +
'Mobile: ' + candidateData.mobile + '
' +
'Location: ' + candidateData.currentLocation + '

' +
'Current Position: ' + candidateData.currentDesignation + ' at ' + candidateData.currentCompany + '
' +
'Industry: ' + candidateData.functionalArea + ' | ' + candidateData.industryType + '

' +
'Experience: ' + candidateData.totalExperience + '
' +
'Current CTC: ' + candidateData.currentCTC + '
' +
'Expected CTC: ' + candidateData.expectedCTC + '
' +
'Notice Period: ' + candidateData.noticePeriod + '

' +
'Education:
' +
(candidateData.pgDegree && candidateData.pgDegree !== 'N/A' ? '- ' + candidateData.pgDegree + ' in ' + candidateData.pgSpecialization + ', ' + candidateData.pgInstitute + ' (' + candidateData.pgYear + ')
' : '') +
'- ' + candidateData.ugDegree + ' in ' + candidateData.ugSpecialization + ', ' + candidateData.ugInstitute + ' (' + candidateData.ugYear + ')

' +
'Key Skills: ' + candidateData.keySkills + '

' +
'Summary: ' + candidateData.profileSummary + '

' +
'FULL CV:
' + candidateData.textCv + '

' +
'---

' +
'Format this as a professional resume.

' +
'CRITICAL: Output PLAIN TEXT ONLY. Do NOT use:
' +
'- ** for bold
' +
'- ### for headers
' +
'- --- for dividers
' +
'- Any markdown formatting

' +
'Use ONLY:
' +
'- ALL CAPS for section headers (PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE, EDUCATION, etc.)
' +
'- Blank lines for spacing
' +
'- Bullet points with • character
' +
'- Plain text throughout

' +
'Output the formatted resume text.';

return {
  json: {
    prompt: prompt,
    candidateName: candidateData.name,
    documentId: $('Create a document').item.json.id
  }
};
